      • status

        public int status
        Status of this reward.
        One of the following status codes: UNKNOWN GRANT_REWARD SELF_CLICK ALREADY_CLICKED TOO_MANY_CLICKS EXCEED_MAX_CLICKS_FOR_DAY EXPIRED INVALID_POST
        If status is GRANT_REWARD, the 'reward' field will contain the reward that should be granted.
